Package de.mash1t.networking.packets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectPacket
    Used for establishing a connection
    DisconnectPacket
    Used for closing a connection
    GroupMessagePacket
    Used for group messages
    InfoPacket
    Used to send information (e.g. from Server to client)
    InvalidPacket
    Used as a placeholder for invalid internal results
    KickPacket
    Used for kicking clients
    MessagePacket
    Used as a body for all packets which contain a message (such as InfoPacket)
    Packet
    Used as a body for all other packets
    PrivateMessagePacket
    Used for private messages
    UserListPacket
    Used for a userlist
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PacketType
    Enum for all available packet identifiers If you add a new custom packet, don't forget to add its identifier here
    UserListPacketType
    Enum for all available UserListPacketTypes
